      <title>Newsmax创始人克里斯托弗·鲁迪（Christopher Ruddy），前邮政记者，现在是亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/newsmax-founder-ruddy-ex-ny-post-journalist-is-now-billionaire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Newsmax Inc.作为上市公司的首次亮相，在其股票飙升735％之后，创始人兼首席执行官克里斯托弗·鲁迪（Christopher Ruddy）的财富约为33亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/newsmax-founder-ruddy-ex-ny-post-journalist-is-now-billionaire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:04:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
